 Homecoming]]''\n**Track: [[Ace Hood]] - \"Don't Get Caught Slippin\"\n*''[[America's Best Dance Crew]]''\n**Track: [[Flo Rida]] - \"Rewind\"<small> (featuring [[Wyclef Jean]])</small> \n*[[American Broadcasting Company|ABC]]'s [[NBA Finals]] \n**Track: [[DJ Khaled]] \u2013 \"Victory\" <small>(featuring [[Nas]] & [[John Legend]])</small>\n*[[American Broadcasting Company|ABC]]'s [[NBA Playoffs]] \n**Track: [[Wale (rapper)|Wale]] \u2013 \"Golden Salvation (Jesus Piece)\"\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist|refs=\n\n<ref name=\"websiteyoutube\">\n{{cite news\n| title       =Lee Major Producing \"Free Mason\"\n| first       =\n| last        =\n| url         =https://www.youtube.com/watch?v2Yfx8qtX6YE \n| publisher   =youtube.com\n| date        =\n| accessdate  = 1 May 2015\n}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"cistandard\">{{cite news\n |title        = iStandard Exclusive iNterview with Lee Major of The Inkredibles\n |first        = Kristen Teesdale\n |last         = Frankie P\n |url          = http://istandardproducers.com/interviews/leemajor/\n |publisher    = istandardproducers.com\n |date         = August 24, 2010\n |accessdate   = 2015-07-04\n |archive-url  = https://web.archive.org/web/20150704213339/http://istandardproducers.com/interviews/leemajor/\n |archive-date = July 4, 2015\n |url-status   = dead\n}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"umusicpub\">[http://www.umusicpub.com/#contentRequest=artistdetail&contentLocation=sub&contentOptions=%26artistid%3D5788 Lee Major biography], umusicpub.com, retrieved 3 July 2015</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"savantsoundzllc.blogspot\">{{cite web|last=Bland |first=Bridget |url=http://savantsoundzllc.blogspot.com/2010_07_01_archive.html |title=Rio's World of Music: July 2010 |publisher=Savantsoundzllc.blogspot.com |date=2010-07-26 |accessdate=2014-08-10}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"rossnguyen\">{{cite web|last1=Nguyen|first1=Duy|title=BTS: Rick Ross - Free Mason Ft. Jay Z|url=http://hiphopmakers.com/lee-major-producing-rick-rosss-free-mason|website=HipHopMakers.com|publisher=Hi