0s/'90s; now v23)\n* [[Ultra Vivid Scene]] (disbanded)\n* [[Underground Lovers]] (active)\n* [[Unrest (band)|Unrest]] (disbanded)\n* [[Vaughan Oliver]] & v23 (active)\n* [[M Ward]] (active)\n* [[Wolf & Cub]] (active)\n* [[The Wolfgang Press]] (disbanded)\n* [[Xmal Deutschland]] (disbanded)\n* [[Zomby]] (active)\n|}\n\n== Selected discography ==\n'''2019'''\n# [[Gene Clark]], ''[[No Other]]'' (1974; reissue, 4AD 0070)\n# [[The National (band)|The National]], ''[[I Am Easy to Find (album)|I Am Easy To Find]]'', (4AD0154)\n# [[Holly Herndon]], ''[[Proto (Holly Herndon album)|Proto]]'' (4AD0140)\n# [[Big Thief]], ''[[U.F.O.F.]]'' (4AD0129)\n# [[Aldous Harding]], ''[[Designer (album)|Designer]]'' (4AD0008)\n# [[Deerhunter]], ''[[Why Hasn't Everything Already Disappeared?]]'' (4AD0089)\n\n'''2018'''\n# [[Daughter (band)|Ex:Re]], ''[[Daughter (band)#Music from Before the Storm and Ex:Re|Ex:Re]]'' (4AD0132)\n# [[The Lemon Twigs]], ''[[Go to School]]'' (4AD0094)\n# [[Gang Gang Dance]], ''[[Kazuashita]]'' (4AD0079)\n# [[The Breeders]], ''[[All Nerve]]'' (4AD0035)\n# [[U.S. Girls]], ''[[In a Poem Unlimited]]'' (4AD0046)\n# [[Tune-Yards]], ''[[I Can Feel You Creep Into My Private Life]]'' (4AD0052)\n\n'''2017'''\n# [[The National (band)|The National]], ''[[Sleep Well Beast]]'' (4AD0020)\n# [[Future Islands]], ''[[The Far Field (album)|The Far Field]]'' (4AD0001)\n# [[Sufjan Stevens]], [[Bryce Dessner]], [[Nico Muhly]], James McAlister,  ''[[Planetarium (album)|Planetarium]]'' (4AD0009)\n# [[Aldous Harding]], ''[[Party (Aldous Harding album)|Party]]'' (4AD0008)\n# [[Methyl Ethel]], ''Everything Is Forgotten'' (CAD 3701)\n# [[SOHN (musician)|SOHN]], ''Rennen'' (CAD3708)\n\n'''2016'''\n# [[Atlas Sound]], ''[[Let the Blind Lead Those Who Can See but Cannot Feel]]'' (CAD 3605)\n# [[Daughter (band)|Daughter]], ''[[Not to Disappear]]'' (CAD 3604)\n# [[The Lemon Twigs]], ''[[Do Hollywood]]'' (CAD 3650)\n# [[D.D Dumbo]], ''[[Utopia Defeated]]'' (CAD3616)\n# [[Tim Hecker]], ''[[Love Streams (album)|Love Streams]]'' (CAD3616)\n# [[Scott Walker (singer)|Scott Walker]], ''[[The Childhood of a Leader (film)|The Childhood of a Leader OST]]'' (CAD3620)\n\n'''2015'''\n# [[Purity Ring (band)|Purity Ring]], ''[[Another Eternity]]'' (CAD 3501)\n# [[Grimes (musician)|Grimes]], ''[[Art Angels]]'' (CAD 3535)\n# [[Holly Herndon]], ''[[Platform (album)|Platform]]'' (CAD 3503)\n# [[Deerhunter (band)|Deerhunter]], ''[[Fading Frontier]]'' (CAD 3521)\n# [[U.S. Girls]], ''[[Half Free]]'' (CAD 3520)\n# [[Beirut (band)|Beirut]], ''[[No No No (Beirut album)|No No No]]'' (CAD 3525)\n# [[EL VY]], ''[[Return to the Moon]]'' (CAD 3530)\n\n'''2014'''\n# [[Future Islands]], ''[[Singles (Future Islands album)|Singles]]'' (CAD 3402)\n# [[Sohn (musician)|SOHN]], ''[[Tremors (Sohn album)|Tremors]]'' (CAD 3403)\n# [[Tune-Yards]], ''[[Nikki Nack]]'' (CAD 3414)\n# Merchandise, ''After the End'' (CAD 3430)\n# [[Ariel Pink]], ''Pom Pom'' (CAD 3440)\n\n'''2013'''\n# [[Daughter (band)|Daughter]], ''[[If You Leave (album)|If You Leave]]'' (CAD 3301)\n# [[Iron & Wine]], ''[[Ghost on Ghost]]'' (CAD 3306)\n# [[Deerhunter (band)|Deerhunter]], ''[[Monomania (Deerhunter album)|Monomania]]'' (CAD 3307)\n# [[The National (band)|The National]], ''[[Trouble Will Find Me]]'' (CAD 3315)\n# [[Camera Obscura (band)|Camera Obscura]], ''[[Desire Lines]]'' (CAD 3314)\n\n'''2012'''\n# [[Mark Lanegan Band]], ''[[Blues Funeral]]'' (CAD 3202)\n# [[Grimes (musician)|Grimes]], ''[[Visions (Grimes album)|Visions]]'' (CAD 3208)\n# [[Purity Ring (band)|Purity Ring]], ''[[Purity Ring (band)#Shrines|Shrines]]'' (CAD 3218)\n# [[David Byrne]] & [[St. Vincent (musician)|St. Vincent]], ''[[Love This Giant]]'' (CAD 3231)\n# [[Scott Walker (singer)|Scott Walker]], ''[[Bish Bosch]]'' (CAD 3220)\n\n'''2011'''\n# [[Iron & Wine]], ''[[Kiss Each Other Clean]]'' (CAD 3103)\n# [[Tune-Yards]], ''[[Whokill]]'' (CAD 3106)\n# [[Bon Iver]], ''[[Bon Iver (album)|Bon Iver]]'' (CAD 3117)\n# [[St. Vincent (musician)|St. Vincent]], ''[[St