-stadium.svg|150px]]||Al-Baath Sports City Stadium||400||none||[[Homs]]||\n|-\n|40||[[File:Gfi-set01-stadium.svg|150px]]||Saraqib Municipal Stadium||300||[[Saraqib SC|Saraqib]]||[[Saraqib]]||2010\n|}\n\n==Future stadiums==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n!#!!Image!!Stadium!!Capacity!!Home team!!City!!To be opened\n|-\n|1||[[File:Gfi-set01-stadium.svg|150px]]||[[Deir ez-Zor Sports City Stadium]]||30,000||none||[[Deir ez-Zor]]||TBD\n|-\n|2||[[File:Gfi-set01-stadium.svg|150px]]||[[Al-Rastan Municipal Stadium]]||15,000||none||[[Al-Rastan]]||TBD\n|}\n\n==See also==\n*[[List of association football stadiums by capacity]]\n\n{{Football in Syria}}\n{{Asia topic|List of football stadiums in}}\n\n[[Category:Football venues in Syria|*]]\n[[Category:Lists of association football stadiums|Syria]]\n[[Category:Association football in Syria lists|Stadiums]]\n[[Category:Lists of buildings and structures in Syria|Football stadiums]]\n\n\n==Sources==\n\n* [http://www.gsf-sport.com/?page_id=1030]\n", "text_old": "{{short description|Wikimedia list article}}\nThe following is a '''list of [[football (soccer)|football]] [[stadiums]] in [[Syria]]''' sorted by their capacities.\n\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n!#!!Image!!Stadium!!Capacity!!Home team!!City!!Opened\n|-\n|1||[[File:Aleppo International Stadium, day view, 2009 (2).jpg|150px]]||[[Aleppo International Stadium]]||53,200||none||[[Aleppo]]||2007\n|-\n|2||[[File:Latakia Sports City Stadium.jpg|150px]]||[[Latakia Sports City Stadium]]||45,000||none||[[Latakia]]||1987\n|-\n|3||[[File:AL Karama stadium.jpg|150px]]||[[Khalid ibn al-Walid Stadium]]||32,000||none||[[Homs]]||1960\n|-\n|4||[[File:Abbasiyyin stadium from a distance.jpg|150px]]||[[Abbasiyyin Stadium]]||30,000||none||[[Damascus]]||1957\n|-\n|5||[[File:Al assad stadium latakia.jpg|150px]]||[[Al-Assad Stadium]]||28,000||[[Tishreen SC|Tishreen]], [[Hutteen SC|Hutteen]]||[[Latakia]]||1978\n|-\n|6||[[File:Basel al-Assad stadium, al-Hasakah.jpg|150px]]||[[Bassel al-Assad Stadiu